dmca.title: TV DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google: Android Market

works.description:
The Moron Test is a simple brain teaser  
game, which has been out for about 2 years as an application.  It launched
 
May 13th, 2010 in the Android Market and has since become the 5th most  
downloaded paid game in the Marketplace.  The Moron Test consists of 4  
sections, each of which has about 100 steps.  The entire app currently has
 
over 400 steps, all having custom made and taylored questions and graphics
 
designed in-house to be as tricky as possible for users.
